'''Algolia'''是一家[[美国|美国]]的[[创业公司|创业公司]]，通过[[SaaS|SaaS]]（软件即服务）模式提供网络搜索产品。

== 发展历史 ==
Algolia由来自[[法国|法国]][[巴黎|巴黎]]的萨科·德赛妮和朱利安·勒莫瓦纳于2012年创办，初期时的主要业务是在手机上进行离线搜索，在欧洲和美国各设有两个数据中心。后来它被选为[[Y_Combinator_(公司)|Y Combinator]]<ref name="Techcrunch, Jan 20143">{{Cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2014/01/21/algolia-provides-spotlight-for-the-web-with-its-turbocharged-realtime-search-api/|title=Algolia Provides ‘Spotlight’ For The Web With Its Turbocharged Real-Time Search API|author=Romain Dillet|date=21 January 2014|website=techcrunch.com|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2016-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005100015/https://techcrunch.com/2014/01/21/algolia-provides-spotlight-for-the-web-with-its-turbocharged-realtime-search-api/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年冬季课程的一部分。2014年3月，Algolia在新加坡开设了第三个中心。<ref name="Techcrunch, Mar 2014">{{Cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2014/03/14/algolia-adds-asian-data-center-while-taking-over-search-on-the-web/|title=Algolia Adds Asian Data Center While Taking Over Search On The Web|author=Romain Dillet|date=21 March 2014|website=techcrunch.com|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2016-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611214029/http://techcrunch.com/2014/03/14/algolia-adds-asian-data-center-while-taking-over-search-on-the-web/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年5月，Algolia获得了1830万美元的A系列投资。<ref name="Algolia Raises $18.3M , Sep 2016">{{Cite web|url=http://www.marketwired.com/press-release/algolia-raises-183m-series-a-investment-led-by-accel-partners-2021539.htm|title=Algolia Raises $18.3M Series A Investment Led by Accel Partners|date=11 September 2016|website=builtwith.com|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2017-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170323033539/http://www.marketwired.com/press-release/algolia-raises-183m-series-a-investment-led-by-accel-partners-2021539.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>自2016年6月起，小型网站对Algolia的使用开始显着增加。<ref name="statistics, Sep 2016">{{Cite web|url=http://trends.builtwith.com/widgets/Algolia|title=Algolia Usage Statistics|date=11 September 2016|website=builtwith.com|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2016-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160921005610/http://trends.builtwith.com/widgets/Algolia|dead-url=no}}</ref>

现在Algolia已在15个地区设立了47个数据中心。<ref name="Website, Sep 2016">{{Cite web|url=https://www.algolia.com/infra|title=Algolia's website|date=11 September 2016|website=algolia.com|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2016-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161117000055/https://www.algolia.com/infra|dead-url=no}}</ref>它为1600多个客户提供服务，每月要处理120亿个用户的查询请求，<ref name="wavefront">{{Cite web|url=https://www.wavefront.com/how-algolia-uses-wavefront-hosted-search-api/|title=How Algolia Uses Wavefront to Keep Its Hosted Search API Instantaneous for 12B+ Queries Monthly|author=Caroline Kunz|date=July 22, 2016|website=wavefront.com|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2016-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230032226/https://www.wavefront.com/how-algolia-uses-wavefront-hosted-search-api/|dead-url=no}}</ref>客户主要来自电子商务等领域。<ref name="about Algolia, Sep 2016">{{Cite web|url=https://www.algolia.com/about|title=About Algolia|date=11 September 2016|website=algolia.com|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2016-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161117000320/https://www.algolia.com/about|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 融资历史 ==

*2013年10月-2014年6月，在种子轮融资中，Algolia先后3次共募集了近300万美元资金，投资者包括 Storm Ventures、Y Combinator、The Family、500 Startups、Index Ventures、Point Nine、LocalGlobe、Alven、Initialized Capital、Acequia Capital (AceCap)、Storm Ventures、Zillionize等。<ref name="Algoliahistory">{{Cite web |url=https://www.mg21.com/algolia.html |title=通过搜索即服务(Search-as-a-Service)提供网络搜索产品的平台：Algolia, Inc. |publisher=美股之家 |date=2021-06-17 |access-date=2021-06-18 |archive-date=2021-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210630015158/https://www.mg21.com/algolia.html }}</ref>。
*2015年5月，A轮融资，Algolia获得Accel Partners领投，Storm Ventures、Point Nine、Alven、Lead Edge Capital等跟投的1830万美元投资。
*2017年6月，B轮融资，Algolia获得Accel Partners领投，Storm Ventures、Point Nine、Alven、Initialized Capital等跟投的5300万美元投资。<ref name="Algoliahistory"/>
*2017年9月，Algolia通过二级市场获得 Aglaé Ventures 独家投资。<ref name="Algoliahistory"/>
*2019年10月，C轮融资，Algolia获得Accel Partners领投，Salesforce Ventures、DAG Ventures、Alven、World Innovation Lab (WiL)等跟投的1亿美元投资。

== 产品与技术 ==
[[File:Algolia网页.jpg|缩略图]]
Algolia使用外部托管的搜索引擎为客户的网站提供网络搜索服务。<ref name="leanstack">{{Cite web|url=http://thenewstack.io/algolia-takes-app-search-new-places/|title=How Algolia Built Their Realtime Search as a Service Product|author=Leanstack|date=March 23, 2014|website=thenewstack.io|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2016-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013234048/http://thenewstack.io/algolia-takes-app-search-new-places/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Interview with the CEO of search powerhouse, Algolia">{{Cite web|url=http://vator.tv/news/2016-07-29-interview-with-the-ceo-of-search-powerhouse-algolia#UgLVz21sHlX0jxAy.99|title=Interview with the CEO of search powerhouse, Algolia|author=Josiah Motley|date=July 29, 2016|website=vator.tv|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2017-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170422022534/http://vator.tv/news/2016-07-29-interview-with-the-ceo-of-search-powerhouse-algolia#UgLVz21sHlX0jxAy.99|dead-url=no}}</ref>产品只需索引客户的网站里的内容，因此搜索任务要简单得多。

Algolia声称他们的搜索技术有很多优点，<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://blog.leanstack.io/how-algolia-built-their-realtime-search-as-a-service-product#origins|title=How Algolia Built Their Realtime Search as a Service Product|date=23 March 2014|website=leanstack.io|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2014-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018032238/http://blog.leanstack.io/how-algolia-built-their-realtime-search-as-a-service-product#origins|dead-url=no}}</ref>例如响应速度。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.algolia.com/features|title=High Performance|website=algolia.com|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2015-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150427065658/http://www.algolia.com/features|dead-url=no}}</ref>Algolia强调他们有即时、多平台和防错的能力。虽然Algolia的软件是封闭源代码，但在一定程度上仍参与了开源社区，因此一些新且有趣的产品从他们的社区纷纷涌现，<ref name="Algolia geosearch">{{Cite web|url=https://www.algolia.com/doc/guides/geo-search/geo-search-overview|title=Algolia Geo-Search|date=11 September 2015|website=algolia.com|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2016-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161012063451/https://www.algolia.com/doc/guides/geo-search/geo-search-overview|dead-url=no}}</ref>例如Algolia Places和Algolia Document。<ref name="Algolia Takes In-App Search to New Places">{{Cite web|url=http://thenewstack.io/algolia-takes-app-search-new-places/|title=Algolia Takes In-App Search to New Places|author=Susan Hall|date=1 Jul 2016|website=thenewstack.io|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2016-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013234048/http://thenewstack.io/algolia-takes-app-search-new-places/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Algolia docsearch">{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/algolia/docsearch-configs|title=Algolia DocSearch|date=11 September 2015|website=github.com|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2018-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627072922/https://github.com/algolia/docsearch-configs|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Algolia还会通过各种API提供其搜索服务。<ref name="github, Sep 2016">{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/algolia|title=Github|date=11 September 2016|website=builtwith.com|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2017-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170104082921/https://github.com/algolia|dead-url=no}}</ref>Rest API提供了搜索、分析和监视三个基本功能，有10种计算机语言和平台可供客户端使用，包括[[Java|Java]]、[[iOS|iOS]]和[[Android|Android]]。为了更好的在Web端使用，Algolia集成了四个框架——Ruby on Rails、Symfony、Django和Laravel。Algolia还提供一些UI库选项来让用户选择他们喜欢的用户界面。除了这些产品，Algolia还与其他开源和第三方软件集成了Wordpress和Magento等服务。<ref name="Algolia API">{{Cite web|url=https://www.algolia.com/doc|title=Algolia API|date=11 September 2015|website=algolia.com|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2016-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161224093306/https://www.algolia.com/doc/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

